+## 3. UI Layout & Visual Design
+
+The UI will be formatted to fit standard $80 \times 24$ terminal windows, but will dynamically adapt if larger screen space is available.
+
+### 3.1 Terminal ASCII / Unicode Grid Layout
+
+```
++-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
+| FREECELL SOLITAIRE                                           [SEED: 49281]  |
+|                                                                             |
+| Free Cells                      Foundations                                 |
+| [A]  [B]  [C]  [D]              [♥]     [♦]     [♣]     [♠]                 |
+| +---+ +---+ +---+ +---+         +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+               |
+| | 5♣| |   | |   | |   |         | A♥|   |   |   |   |   |   |               |
+| +---+ +---+ +---+ +---+         +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+               |
+|                                                                             |
+| Tableau Columns                                                             |
+|  [1]     [2]     [3]     [4]     [5]     [6]     [7]     [8]                |
+| +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+   +---+               |
+| | K♠|   | J♦|   | Q♣|   | 9♦|   | 8♣|   | 6♥|   | 10♦|  | A♠|               |
+| | Q♦|   | 10♣|  | 3♦|   | 8♥|   | 7♦|   | 5♦|   | 9♠|   |   |               |
+| | J♣|   |   |   | 2♠|   |   |   | 6♠|   |   |   |   |   |   |               |
